    <subsection name="jintegers">
      <p>The <var>jintegers</var> package implements a set of functions
      for dealing with integers in Java.</p>
    </subsection>
    <subsection name="Features">
      <ul>
        <li>Functions for packing and unpacking 16, 24, 32, and 64 bit integers in big or little endian order.</li>
        <li>CheckedMath class that signals overflow and underflow at run time.</li>
        <li>Full unit test coverage.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.osgi.org/">OSGi</a>-ready.</li>
        <li>ISC license.</li>
      </ul>
    </subsection>
